ISLAMABAD, May 24 (APP):Chairman Senate Muhammad Sadiq Sanjrani has appreciated Emir of Qatar, Sheikh Tamim bin Hamad Al-Thani’s stance on Palestine issue.
According to a press release issued here Monday, the Chairman Senate during session, lauded the move of Emir of Qatar and said that the position taken by the Emir on the issue of Palestine is not only an expression of the Muslim Ummah but also a desire of every Muslim’s heart. The Emir of Qatar always takes a pragmatic position, which is commendable, he added.
